{"Title":"黑椒薯块的做法","Primary":["土豆400克"],"Auxiliary":["盐少许","黑胡椒1小勺"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.土豆去皮洗干净","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266846613148.jpg","2.切成滚刀块","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266846649528.jpg","3.炒锅热油，要多一点","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266846980169.jpg","4.放入土豆块","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266847072340.jpg","5.不停地翻动炸熟，（大约5分钟就熟了）","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266847176712.jpg","6.盛出土豆块，撒上一点盐","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266847271913.jpg","7.撒一点黑胡椒粉。拌一下","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266847354084.jpg","8.享用","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266846400704.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266860340870.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266860337059.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266860484558.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_142266860499761.jpg","烹饪技巧","油温7分热的时候放入土豆块，上下翻动，外面微焦，没有硬心就熟透，大约5分钟。炸好后的薯块也可以蘸着椒盐吃。"]}